---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout 
  title="Financial Guidance During Loss | Summit Wealth Advisors" 
  description="Compassionate financial guidance after the loss of a loved one. We provide a clear, simple checklist of immediate steps and long-term financial organization."
>
  <!-- Hero Section -->
  <section class="py-20 md:py-28 bg-primary text-white text-center">
    <div class="container mx-auto px-4">
      <h1 class="text-5xl font-serif font-bold mb-4">Compassionate Guidance in Difficult Times</h1>
      <p class="text-xl text-slate-300 max-w-3xl mx-auto">
        When you're grieving, the last thing you need is financial complexity. We're here to provide a clear, simple path forward.
      </p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Main Content -->
  <section class="py-16 md:py-24 bg-brand-neutral">
    <div class="container mx-auto px-4 max-w-4xl text-lg">
      <div class="prose prose-lg max-w-none text-slate-700 space-y-12">
        <div>
          <h2 class="text-4xl font-serif font-bold text-primary">Immediate Steps: The Next 30 Days</h2>
          <p class="leading-relaxed">
            In the immediate aftermath of a loss, focus on the essential. The goal is not to make major decisions, but to organize and understand the immediate landscape. We can help you create a simple checklist.
          </p>
          <h3 class="text-2xl font-serif font-semibold text-primary mt-6">Key Documents to Locate:</h3>
          <ul class="list-disc pl-5 mt-4 grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-x-8">
            <li>Will and any Trust documents</li>
            <li>Social Security card/number</li>
            <li>Birth and death certificates</li>
            <li>Marriage certificate</li>
            <li>Life insurance policies</li>
            <li>Bank and investment statements</li>
            <li>Recent tax returns</li>
            <li>Real estate deeds</li>
          </ul>
        </div>
        
        <div>
          <h2 class="text-4xl font-serif font-bold text-primary">Long-Term Clarity: Building a New Plan</h2>
          <p class="leading-relaxed">
            Once the immediate needs are met, we can begin the process of creating long-term financial clarity. This is a journey taken at your own pace. We'll help you understand how assets will be retitled, how your income sources may have changed, and how to structure a new financial plan that provides security and confidence for your future. Our role is to simplify the complex so you can focus on what matters most.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Internal Linking -->
  <section class="py-16 bg-brand-neutral border-t border-slate-200">
    <div class="container mx-auto px-4">
      <h3 class="text-2xl font-serif text-center text-primary mb-8">Explore Other Life Transitions</h3>
      <div class="flex justify-center gap-8 text-center">
        <a href="/retirement" class="text-primary hover:text-secondary font-semibold">Find clarity in retirement planning &rarr;</a>
        <a href="/career-changes" class="text-primary hover:text-secondary font-semibold">Navigate a career transition with confidence &rarr;</a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</Layout>
